<item>
            <title>[LU-2224] Missing ZFS osd_commit_async() locking</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-2224</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The ZFS osd_commit_async() implementation in master never properly acquired the tx-&amp;gt;tx_sync_lock() mutex.  Presumably this code is either:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;1) Never/rarely called because it should trigger an ASSERT in the SPL, or&lt;br/&gt;
2) The SPL/ZFS debugging is disabled in the automated testing&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ll follow up shortly with the trivial fix.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
